msgid "Outdated Version"
msgstr "Zastarjela verzija"
msgid ""
"Do you want to proceed with the installation of this old version anyway? BigLinux is a system with "
"weekly updates and this version was released more than a month ago. We recommend downloading a more "
"recent version."
msgstr ""
"Želite li nastaviti s instalacijom ove stare verzije? BigLinux je sustav s tjednim ažuriranjima, a "
"ova verzija je objavljena prije više od mjesec dana. Preporučujemo preuzimanje novije verzije."
